OL,3,C'Set up was a nightmare': Firms under
OL,4,Cpressure as pension deadline looms
OL,6,FSome Guernsey employers are
OL,7,Fquestioning the feasibility of
OL,8,Foffering every worker a secondary
OL,9,Fpension.
OL,11,FBy 1 October, all businesses in the
OL,12,Fisland will have to provide the option
OL,13,Fby law, even if they only have one
OL,14,Femployee, although workers have the
OL,15,Fchoice to opt out.
OL,17,FThe changes have been rolled out in
OL,18,Fphases, starting with larger firms
OL,19,Fneeding to comply by July 2024 and
OL,20,Fthen steadily including smaller
OL,21,Fbusinesses.
