OL,3,C'Set up was a nightmare': Firms under
OL,4,Cpressure as pension deadline looms
OL,6,FIt brings Guernsey in line with the
OL,7,FUK, where the same regulations were
OL,8,Fbrought in more than 10 years ago.
OL,10,FIn Jersey, however, there is currently
OL,11,Fno legislation as plans were delayed
OL,12,Fearlier this year.
OL,14,FPoliticians justify the move by saying
OL,15,Faction needs to be taken now to make
OL,16,Fsure public finances are not
OL,17,Foverstretched by an ageing population
OL,18,Frelying solely on the States in later
OL,19,Flife, but the extra cost for
OL,20,Fbusinesses has not been welcomed by
OL,21,Feveryone.
