OL,3,C'Set up was a nightmare': Firms under
OL,4,Cpressure as pension deadline looms
OL,6,FPaul Langmead, who runs a Guernsey
OL,7,Fwindow-fitting company, says: "Trying
OL,8,Fto get it set up was a nightmare.
OL,9,FPlus, now trying to remember to do
OL,10,Fyour payment and template every month
OL,11,Fis very awkward.
OL,13,F"You've got freight and extra tipping
OL,14,Fcosts now, so all those costs mount
OL,15,Fup."
OL,17,FBefore secondary pensions were
OL,18,Fintroduced, 65% of the working-age
OL,19,Fpopulation in Guernsey had not saved
OL,20,Ffor retirement.
