OL,3,C'Set up was a nightmare': Firms under
OL,4,Cpressure as pension deadline looms
OL,6,FThere will be an estimated 5,500 extra
OL,7,Fpensioners in Guernsey by 2040, with
OL,8,Fthe prescribed government money
OL,9,Fsupporting them expected to run out at
OL,10,Fthe same time.
OL,12,FPoliticians have discussed whether
OL,13,Fislanders should be forced to put
OL,14,Fmoney aside, like in Australia and
OL,15,FSwitzerland, but decided against it
OL,16,Ffor now.
