OL,3,C'Set up was a nightmare': Firms under
OL,4,Cpressure as pension deadline looms
OL,6,FRebecca Goater, a local financial
OL,7,Fadviser, explains: "I think one of the
OL,8,Fthings that may catch people out is
OL,9,Fthat even people on zero-hour
OL,10,Fcontracts could be eligible to need a
OL,11,Fsecondary pension scheme.
OL,13,F"If you have any employees who earn
OL,14,Fover the minimum lower limits for
OL,15,FSocial Security, they'll potentially
OL,16,Fbe eligible."
